review: My father was suffering from heart issue, swelling in leg and severe breathing issue, we consulted to Dr. Rockey Katheria, he helped us to understand the main problem. listened patiently and diagnosed right way, my father is feeling well now and swelling leg, berating issue has gone, he called us after 15 days, we visited again, he changes the medicine does and ask again to come after few month, he is very friendly and helping nature, god bless him, My father is priest and blessing him a lot,
*** ** *** **** *********.he handled my husband case so smoothly and efficiently and explained in detail.he was such a positive doctor we felt very comfortable.

He doesn’t even care to listen to patients issue in the first stance

I found it very rude
Won’t recommend

**** *** ******* ***** *** ** ***** *** ********* He is way too rude and arrogant to be a Doctor. He got me wait for really long and ended up without a consultation even after charging the amount. People should really refrain since they would be getting misleaded. Wont recommend at all.
A  very nice person understands the patient patiently Talks to the point and sees that he has conveyed it to patient understanding
Friendly communication skill, explaining the factors  as live as appearance, and easy to mingle with.

Doctor patiently attended to my issues and concerns and was very assuring and friendly .

Very satisfied with my visit. 

Much recommended.
**** ******. Explains properly.  Do recommend adequate tests and medicines but not unnecessary tests.
Such a beautiful and friendly doctor very good person I have highly recommended this doctor for cardiac issue for me he treated very well

review: He was very patient in discussing the symptoms and analysis as well as the next steps on treating it. Explained the risks and the care to be taken while following the prescribed medicine and the lifestyle changes required.Very responsive.
